        "description": "Solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2) is a commercial FDA-recognized tool with documented version control. Internal SQA log maintained. Achieved Gradation 2 despite ~50% confidence in completeness of audit trail; shortfall is disclosed and bounded by independent code-verification sweep."
