      "rationale": "Commercial CFD solver with documented release notes and version pinning satisfies Gradation 1. Internal SQA log covers mesh generation and boundary-condition scripts. Confidence in audit-trail completeness is approximately 50% due to partial documentation of turbulence-model selection history; this limitation is explicitly disclosed. Achieved level 2 is supported by two independent reviewers cross-checking input decks."
