        "description": "Solver passes FDA benchmark hemolysis test suite (lid-driven cavity, backward-facing step). Confidence ~50% that all relevant flow regimes are covered; wide bounds on turbulence-model benchmark coverage are disclosed."
      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent passes the FDA-published benchmark suite for internal blood-flow solvers. However, the benchmark suite does not include rotating-frame centrifugal cases at all five operating points. Confidence that numerical errors are fully bounded is approximately 50%; this is honestly documented. Gradation 2 is justified by the rotating-frame MRF verification study conducted in-house, which showed residuals < 1e-5 for all cases."
