        "name": "Validation geometry and flow conditions overlap COU domain — Gradation 2",
        "description": "Validation experiments performed on the same FDA generic pump geometry under CPB-representative flow conditions (2–6 L/min, 3500–5000 RPM). Confidence ~50% that all COU-relevant operating points are covered."
      },
      "rationale": "Validation experiments were conducted on the identical FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under CPB-representative conditions spanning the full COU operating range. Confidence in coverage is approximately 50% because only 5 of a possible 25 flow-speed combinations were tested experimentally. This sampling limitation is disclosed; the 5 points were selected by Latin hypercube design to maximize coverage of the operating envelope. Achieved level 2 is supported by the structured experimental design."
    },
    {
